metadata.description: Furry Citizens  - NFT collection of animals living in Kurio - the futuristic city of 2132. It contains 3 districts: Takurra - a place full of blooming greenery, where the peaceful inhabitants of the city live; Sutzo - the business center of the capital, filled with ambitious and evil individuals; Bolton - violent area where hundreds of crimes occur every day.
metadata.name: Furry Citizens #1
